data.value: The Asus ROG Rapture GT-AX11000 Pro Tri-Band Gigabit WiFi Gaming Router eliminates lag and latency. This tri-band router, which is primarily aimed at gamers and enthusiasts looking to optimize their high-speed internet and network device connections, takes Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) performance to the next level with up to 10,756 Mb/s total wireless data throughput. At the same time, RangeBoost Plus technology aids in coverage expansion, while built-in game acceleration capabilities enhance online gaming experiences.The Asus ROG Rapture GT-AX11000 Pro Tri-Band Gigabit WiFi Gaming Router By taking advantage of the 160 MHz channel, the ROG GT-AX11000 Pro delivers up to 4804 Mb/s data transfers on each of its two 5 GHz bands with compatible devices while the 2.4 GHz frequency supports 1148 Mb/s.
